name: Neuromuscular Power #2
description:
After warming up, set your pace at a lower end Tempo effort for the next 50 minutes. Within these 50 minutes, you will be performing a 10 second out of the saddle sprint every 5 minutes. Aim for a high cadence in sprints with 1 - 2 gear changes into a harder gear during the effort. 



Can you hit the same Peak Power for all ten sprints?
